How does it feel to sit at the VIP box of the legendary San Siro stadium, wear a nice suit, and see the player you have discovered when he was just 15, Mavis Tchibota, go up against Romelu Lukaku and Christian Eriksen? You can ask Stari’s Founder, Mr. Avi Zioni. The most incredible part – he didn’t have any scouting background! Avi was a regular fan, watching football games on television and loving statistics, but most importantly, knowing who will become an amazing player, because he had an eye for identifying talent. Who says you can’t do the same?  
