How to do this? When it comes to scouting in 2022, football fans with passion and good eye for talents aren’t involved in the game and influence it. Stari offers them the option to become a “fan-scout” in their country and use knowledge of local football to make extra money from simply doing what they love: watching football! How to become a fan-scout? Stari offers a fast track to become a professional scout: install our app and become an active user there – rate videos and prove that you can see talent, get access to the exclusive platform Stari Pro, and become a part of Stari team to work with us, make money and have promotion opportunities for jobs at European clubs. Get it here: IOS  Android
