If I don’t have a lot of time, but love football and want to make money out of it? Stari has a new mobile app, currently exclusive to Africa, where players can create profiles and upload football videos, to be rated by thousands of fans. Any parent, friend, or player himself, can see the benefits in using the app. Footballers with top ratings will be noticed by hundreds of scouts and have professional trials in Europe. Fans who identified the talents have the benefits of rewards like cash prizes, flights to games in Europe, job opportunities and access to the next football stars. What if I want to become a professional scout? Another Stari feature is our Master Scouting Course. We have invested many resources to promote African football by building this study program – to help fans learn to be scouts, become professionals, and advance their careers. The course is presented by scouts and other professionals, working for the biggest football clubs in the world, and who discovered amazing talents over their careers. After the course, you will get job opportunities, connections to clubs and a free subscription to the Stari Pro platform. What is the Stari Pro platform? On Stari Pro platform, professional scouts and fan-scouts, called Commando Scouts, are watching games from under-the-radar leagues and tournaments. After spotting the best undiscovered young talents, they write and submit analytical reports. These reports are judged by Stari’s professional committee, formed by veteran scouts, sport directors and journalists. The best scouts are awarded points with which they can win amazing prizes, like big financial rewards or flying out to watch Champions League matches. The best prize of all? Full time scouting job at Stari or in one of Stari’s partner clubs in Europe. How is Stari different? Stari is different because we offer several career and entertainment options for all football lovers – fans, scouts, and players. Our network of partner football clubs and other connections all over the world, but mainly in Africa and Europe, makes it possible for us to launch your football career, straight from the couch to the stars. Besides the human connection, we have several technological tools, with hundreds of thousands of dollars invested in them, all designed to make your football dreams come true. In addition, our activity helps African football grow and show the world the value of African players.  Unlike others, we believe that developing local sports is a priority, since it helps so many people with their lives. We believe that with our help you can make it in football. Do you believe in yourself? Get it here: IOS  Android 